<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Error</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #2980b9; /* 3D Blue color */
            color: #333; /* Darker text color for better visibility */
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .error-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #ff5252; /* Red color */
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .center {
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <h1 class="center">Error</h1>
        <p>An unexpected error occurred. Please try again later, Try some different approach</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
